1. gxf4 Nxh4! 2. Kf2 Nf5 3. Kf3 Nd6 { Force white's knight on a bad spot } { [%csl Ge6] } 4. Na3 Kd5 5. Kg3 Nf5+ 6. Kf3 Kc5 7. Kg2 Kc6 8. Kf2 Kd5 9. Kf3 Nd6 10. Kg3 Nf5+ 11. Kf3 Kc6 12. Kg2 h4! 13. Kh3 Kd5 { All black's pieces are stuck defending black's pawns } 14. Kg4 Ke4 15. c4 Kd4! { 0-1 } { [%cal Gd4c5,Gc5b4] } *


