1. g4 Nd4 2. h4 { [%csl Gh5][%cal Gh4h5] } 2... Ke7 3. Bb7 { stops b6-b5 } { [%csl Gd6] } 3... a5 { [%csl Ga6,Gb5,Gc6,Gd5] } 4. Bd5 Be5 5. Be4 { Before launching the plan, play semi-waiting move to see how opponent respond } 5... Ne6 6. Kf3 Bf6 7. g5! { Keep black's pieces unfree } 7... Be5 8. Kg4 Bd4 9. f4 { [%cal Gf4f5] } 9... f5+ 10. gxf6+ Kxf6 11. f5! { sideline pass ed pawn is always strong } 11... gxf5+ 12. Bxf5 Ng7 13. Bg5+ Kf7 14. Bd7! Ne6 15. Bxe6+! Kxe6 16. Bd8 a4 17. Bxb6 d5 18. cxd5+ Kxd5 19. Kf5 axb3 20. axb3 *


