1. d4 d5 2. c4 c6 3. cxd5 cxd5 4. Nf3 Nf6 5. Nc3 Nc6 6. Bf4 Ne4 7. e3 Nxc3 8. bxc3 g6 9. Be2 Bg7 10. O-O O-O 11. c4 dxc4 12. Bxc4 Bf5 13. Rc1 Rc8 { [%cal Gb7b3,Ga7a3] } 14. Qe2 a6 15. h3?! { If white fails to use his 5-4 majority on centre and kingside and black use his 2-1 majority in queenside, then black is in effect a pawn up } (15. d5! Na5 16. e4!) 15... Na5! 16. Bd3 Bxd3 17. Qxd3 { Force the trade of good bishops to seize control of the c4 square } 17... Qd7! { 在发动机话以前不要着急,先把子处理好 } (17... b5? 18. Rxc8 Qxc8 19. Qa3!) 18. Rc3 b5 { [%csl Gd4,Gc4][%cal Ga5c4] } 19. Rfc1 Nc4 20. Qe2 Nb6 21. Rc7 Qe6 22. Bg5 Nd5 23. R7c5 h6 24. Bh4 { [%csl Gc3] } 24... b4 25. Qb2 Nc3 26. Rxc8 Rxc8 27. Kh1 Kh7!! { If two rooks are contesting an open file, the player with superior minor piece will win control of it.
The point is to escape the check on c8, so that Na4 can be threatened } { [%csl Gc1,Gc8,Gc3,Gg7,Ga4][%cal Gc8c1,Gc3a4] } 28. Ra1 a5 29. Qb3 Qxb3 30. axb3 g5 31. Bg3 a4! 32. Nd2 a3 33. Rc1 { [%csl Gg7,Gd4,Ge3][%cal Gg7d4] } 33... e5! { What is the worst placed piece? g7 bishop } 34. d5 a2 35. Ra1 e4 36. d6 Ra8 37. Nc4 Nb5 38. Be5 Nxd6! 39. Rxa2 Rxa2 40. Bxd6 Rxf2 41. Bxb4 Rf1+ 42. Kh2 Rb1 { 0-1
如果不积极利用majority,对面就会赢
一定要耐心、淡定。实行计划以前和petrosian一样走半等招,同时子出完,确保这个计划在现在是最强的然后再走。 } *


