1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 Bb4 4. Qc2 O-O 5. a3 Bxc3+ 6. Qxc3 b6 7. Bg5 Bb7 8. f3 h6 9. Bh4 d5 10. e3 Nbd7 11. cxd5 Nxd5 12. Bxd8 Nxc3 13. Bh4 Nd5 { [%csl Ge4,Gf4] } 14. Bf2 { [%csl Ga7][%cal Gf2b6] } 14... c5 { [%csl Gd4] } 15. e4 Ne7 16. Ne2 Rac8 17. Nc3 cxd4 18. Bxd4 Nc5 19. Rd1 Rfd8 20. Be3 Rxd1+ 21. Kxd1 e5 22. b4 Ne6 23. Kc2 Nc6 24. Kb2 { [%csl Gb6,Ga7][%cal Ge3a7] } 24... Kf8 25. Bc4 { [%csl Gc6] } 25... Ncd4 26. Bxe6 Nxe6 { [%csl Gb6,Ga7,Ge4,Gf3,Gg2,Ge3,Gb7] } 27. Nb5 Ra8 28. a4! Ba6 29. Na3 { [%csl Gc4][%cal Ga6c4] } 29... Rc8 30. b5! Bb7 31. Rc1! Rxc1 32. Kxc1 Ke7 33. a5! bxa5 34. Bxa7 f5 35. exf5 Nf4 36. g3 Nh3 37. Nc4 Ng5 38. Nxa5 Bd5 39. b6 Nxf3 40. h3 Ng5 41. b7 Bxb7 42. Nxb7 Nxh3 43. Bb6! { The idea is to stop Kf6. Ng5 is also indirectly stopped } { [%csl Gf6,Gd8][%cal Gh3g5,Ge7f6,Gb6d8] } 43... Kd7 44. Be3! { Now the king does not go to f6 } 44... Ke7 45. Nc5 { [%csl Gf6,Gf4,Gg4,Gh5,Ge4] } 45... g6 46. fxg6 Kf6 47. Bxh6 Kxg6 48. Be3 { 1--0 } { [%csl Gd3][%cal Gg6f5] } 48... Kf5 { [%csl Gd3,Gg4,Ge5] } 49. Kd2 Kg4 50. Ne4 { [%csl Gh3][%cal Ge4f6,Gg3g4,Gg4g5,Gh3g5,Gh3f4,Gh3f2,Gh3g1] } *


