{ Play against weaknesses with active pieces. Cat and mouse game, inducing weaknesses and make use of it. }
1. c4 g6 2. e4 Bg7 3. d4 d6 4. Nc3 Nc6 5. Be3 e5 6. d5 Nce7 7. c5 f5 8. cxd6 cxd6 9. Bb5+! { [%csl Ge4,Gd5,Gb5] } 9... Bd7? (9... Kf8) 10. Bxd7+ Qxd7 11. f3 Nf6 12. Nh3! h6 13. Nf2 O-O 14. Qa4! Qxa4 15. Nxa4 Rac8 16. Nc3 a6 17. Ke2! Kh7 18. Rac1 Nd7 { 马在打b7-a6结构时候去c4比较多 } { [%csl Gg7,Gd6,Ge4,Ge3,Gc3,Ge7,Gb1][%cal Gc3b1] } 19. Nb1! Rxc1 20. Rxc1 Rc8 21. Na3 Rxc1 22. Bxc1 h5 23. Nc4 Nc8 24. Bd2 { With Bb4, eliminating black's g7 bishop } { [%csl Gb4][%cal Gd2b4] } 24... Bf6 25. Na5! b6 26. Nc6 Kg7 27. Be3 Kf7 { [%csl Gc6] } 28. Nd3 Ke8 29. a4! { Inducing black to play a7-a5 and weakening the position. } 29... Bd8 { [%csl Ga5] } 30. Ndb4! { [%csl Ga5][%cal Ga6a5] } 30... a5 31. Na2!! { Now after inducing a6-a5, the knight goes to b5 } { [%csl Gb5][%cal Ga2c3,Gc3b5] } 31... f4 32. Bf2 g5 33. Kd3! { King going to a6 before Na2-c3-b5 } 33... Nf8 34. h3 Ng6 { [%csl Ga6,Gb5][%cal Ga2c3,Gc3b5] } 35. Nc3 Bf6 36. Kc4 Kd7 37. Kb5 Kc7 38. Ka6 g4 39. hxg4 hxg4 40. fxg4 Bh4 { [%csl Gb5][%cal Gc3b5] } 41. Nd1! { Preventing all kinds of threat against g2 } 41... Bxf2 42. Nxf2 Nce7 (42... Nh4 43. g5 Ng6 44. Nd3 { [%csl Gf3][%cal Gd3e1,Ge1f3] }) 43. Nxe7 Nxe7 44. g5 Ng6 45. Ng4 Nh4 46. Ka7 Ng6 47. Nh2! { Now black is forced to Zugzwang } { [%csl Gh4][%cal Gh2f3,Gf3h4] } 47... Nh4 48. Nf3! Ng6 49. b3! { 1-0 Beautiful ending. } { [%csl Gg6][%cal Gg6e7,Gf3h4] } *


