1. e4 d5 2. exd5 Nf6 3. d4 Nxd5 4. Nf3 (4. c4 Nf6 5. Nc3 e5) 4... Bg4 5. Be2 c6 6. O-O e6 7. c4 Nf6 8. Nc3 Nbd7 9. h3 Bh5 10. Bf4 (10. d5! exd5 11. cxd5 Bc5 12. dxc6 bxc6 13. Nh4 Bg6 14. Bf3 O-O $14) 10... Nb6 { Eliminate d5 } 11. Qd3 (11. d5 exd5 12. cxd5 Nbxd5) 11... Be7 12. Rad1 O-O 13. Ne5 (13. Rfe1 Bg6 14. Qe3 Nbd7 15. Nh4 { I prefer this plan. keep the light-square bishop and trade opponent’s with the knight. }) 13... Bxe2 14. Qxe2 Nc8! { Trying to get the queen to a5 } 15. Rd3! { Still trying d4-d5 } 15... Qa5 16. a3 Nd6 17. Bg5 Rad8 18. Rfd1 Qa6?! { Idea is to eliminate by attacking on c4 } (18... Rfe8) 19. c5 (19. d5 cxd5 20. cxd5 Nxd5 21. Rxd5 Qxe2 22. Nxe2 f6 23. R5d3 fxg5) (19. Ng4! Kh8 20. Bxf6 Bxf6 (20... gxf6) 21. Nxf6 gxf6 22. Qf3 f5 23. Qe3 Rg8 $14 (23... Qxc4 24. Qe5+ (24. b3 Qa6 25. d5 cxd5 26. Qd4+ (26. Qe5+ f6 27. Qxe6) 26... f6))) 19... Nf5 20. Qf3 Nd5 21. Nxd5 (21. Bxe7 Ndxe7 22. g4 Nh6 23. Ne4 (23. Qe3) 23... f6) 21... Rxd5 22. Bxe7 Nxe7 23. Qe4 Ng6 24. f4 Rfd8 (24... f5 { This is my idea } 25. Qe2 (25. Qf3 Nxe5 26. dxe5 Qa4)) 25. Kh2 Nxe5 26. fxe5 b6! 27. cxb6 axb6 28. Rg3 c5 29. Qh4 g6 30. Rf1 Qxf1 *


